{"tid":1928890,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有時使幾舊水叫雞，只為有人攬下自己","createTime":"2020-03-16T15:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T16:05:16.000Z","uid":58316,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bd671cea67309830913aabb6b749049c4fb40bf2","tid":1928890,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T15:36:40.000Z","msg":"但而家都少去<br />\n係屋企聽住歌<br />\n擺直枕頭<br />\n幻想係女人心口<br />\n自己打側挨住<br />\n環抱住<br />\n合埋眼諗好多野<br />\n其實諗黎有咩用<br />\n都改變唔到<br />\n每日老去<br />\n年華老去<br />\n青春不再<br />\n而家出到街<br />\n唔好話出街<br />\n一踏出房門<br />\n一切都陌生<br />\n好似自己<br />\n無論做咩<br />\n都係錯咁<br />\n無時無刻<br />\n都要為自己所作所為道歉咁<br />\n連就咁生存<br />\n都好似係錯咁<br />\n唯有閂埋房門<br />\n幻想有女攬下自己<br />\n個刻先至自由<br />\n敢同自己講<br />\n其實自己都好辛苦"},{"pid":"0965272b170a1d365e64dc68c5b7becdfdcaadb4","tid":1928890,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T15:56:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PRsdg6Yn0U0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPRsdg6Yn0U0&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebVgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=63ffef49\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PRsdg6Yn0U0</a>"},{"pid":"450be622c7ca828dcd4813fad226864a61eaf71e","tid":1928890,"uid":22188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T16:05:16.000Z","msg":"冇事嫁"}]}